import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"; import "./AdminPage.css" import { Button, Modal } from "react-bootstrap"; function AdminPage() { const [show, setShow] = useState(false); const [data, setData] = useState([]); const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ nume: "", prenume: "", pozitie: "", departament: "", salariu: 0, nivelStudii: "", cnp: "", username: "", password: "", isAdmin: false, isAgentVanzari: false, isContabil: false, isLucratorService: false, }); const handleClose = () => { setShow(false); setFormData({ nume: "", prenume: "", pozitie: "", departament: "", salariu: 0, nivelStudii: "", cnp: "", username: "", password: "", isAdmin: false, isAgentVanzari: false, isContabil: false, isLucratorService: false, }); }; const [deleteCnp, setDeleteCnp] = useState(""); // CNP to delete const [showDeleteConfirmation, setShowDeleteConfirmation] = useState(false); const [searchCNP, setSearchCNP] = useState(""); // State variable for the search input const handleShow = () => setShow(true); const handleSearchInputChange = (e) => { // Update the search input value when the input changes setSearchCNP(e.target.value); }; const filteredData = data.filter((employee) => employee.cnp.includes(searchCNP) ); const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; // For checkboxes, we'll convert the labels back to boolean values if (name === "isAdmin" || name === "isAgentVanzari" || name === "isContabil" || name === "isLucratorService") { setFormData({ ...formData, [name]: !formData[name] }); } else { setFormData({ ...formData, [name]: value }); } }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Make a POST request to your API endpoint fetch("http://localhost:5036/api/DateCompleteAngajat", { method: "POST", headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", }, body: JSON.stringify(formData), }) .then((response) => { if (response.ok) { // Refresh the employee list after successful POST fetch("http://localhost:5036/api/DateCompleteAngajat") .then((response) => response.json()) .then((updatedData) => { setData(updatedData); // Update the data state handleClose(); // Close the modal }) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching updated data:", error)); } else { // Handle errors here } }) .catch((error) => console.error("Error making POST request:", error)); }; useEffect(() => { // Fetch data from your API endpoint fetch("http://localhost:5036/api/DateCompleteAngajat") .then((response) => response.json()) .then((data) => setData(data)) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching data:", error)); }, []); const handleDeleteConfirmation = (cnp) => { // Set the CNP to delete and show the confirmation modal setDeleteCnp(cnp); setShowDeleteConfirmation(true); }; const handleDelete = () => { // Make a DELETE request to your API endpoint using the stored cnpToDelete fetch(`http://localhost:5036/api/DateCompleteAngajat/${deleteCnp}`, { method: "DELETE", }) .then((response) => { if (response.ok) { // Handle successful deletion here, e.g., refresh the employee list // Fetch the updated data and update the 'data' state fetch("http://localhost:5036/api/DateCompleteAngajat") .then((response) => response.json()) .then((updatedData) => setData(updatedData)) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching updated data:", error)); setShowDeleteConfirmation(false); // Close the delete confirmation modal } else { // Handle errors here console.error("Error deleting employee with CNP:", deleteCnp); } }) .catch((error) => console.error("Error making DELETE request:", error));
